Examples

 # gs is a GatingSet
 trans.list <- estimateLogicle(gs[[1]], c("CD3", "CD4", "CD8"))
 # trans.list is a transformerList that can be directly applied to GatinigSet
 gs <- transform(gs, trans.list)
}
